                     <interp inst="t18450818-1563-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="embezzlement"></interp> for embezzling the sums of 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., and 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., which he had received on account of <persName id="t18450818-name-93" type="victimName">
